ZH: 请务必记得把门锁好。
EN: Please remember to lock the door.

ZH: 在使用药物前，务必阅读说明书。
EN: Before using medication, make sure to read the instructions.

ZH: 出行前务必查看天气预报。
EN: Before traveling, be sure to check the weather forecast.

ZH: 学习新技能需要勤奋和务必乐观。
EN: Learning new skills requires diligence and a positive mindset.

ZH: 在交通繁忙的地区，务必小心驾驶。
EN: In busy traffic areas, drive carefully.

ZH: 维护身体健康，务必保持良好的饮食习惯。
EN: To maintain good health, it is essential to have a healthy diet.

ZH: 外出旅行前，务必确认护照和机票是否带上了。
EN: Before going on a trip, make sure to check if you have your passport and tickets.

ZH: 去参加面试之前，务必做好充分的准备。
EN: Before attending an interview, be sure to prepare thoroughly.

ZH: 学习外语需要坚持不懈，务必每天练习。
EN: Learning a foreign language requires perseverance; it is essential to practice every day.

ZH: 遇到困难时，务必保持冷静和乐观的态度。
EN: When faced with difficulties, it is important to stay calm and positive.

ZH: 外出野餐时，务必带上防晒霜和遮阳伞。
EN: When going for a picnic, remember to bring sunscreen and an umbrella.

ZH: 给他人留下一个良好的印象，务必注意自己的举止和言辞。
EN: To leave a good impression on others, pay attention to your behavior and speech.

ZH: 建议在饭前洗手，务必保持卫生。
EN: It is advisable to wash your hands before meals for hygiene reasons.

ZH: 约定好的时间务必准时赴约。
EN: It is crucial to be punctual for appointments at the agreed time.

ZH: 在进行户外运动时，务必注意安全。
EN: When engaging in outdoor activities, it is important to prioritize safety.

ZH: 经济发展必须坚持绿色环保，务必保护环境。
EN: Economic development must adhere to green and sustainable practices; protecting the environment is essential.

ZH: 看医生后，务必按时服药。
EN: After seeing the doctor, make sure to take medications on time.

ZH: 养成良好的睡眠习惯，务必保持充足的睡眠时间。
EN: Develop good sleep habits and ensure you have enough sleep.

ZH: 做任何决定前，务必先深入调查研究。
EN: Before making any decisions, it is vital to conduct thorough research.

ZH: 在学习和工作中，务必养成良好的时间管理习惯。
EN: Developing good time management habits is crucial in both studying and working.
